Arcanium Needle Mace (lvl 51) - spd 3.0 , dps 16.5<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
First of all, the Needle Mace does not sell back to the merchants for the full cost.  There is a 20% loss on sellback.  (Granted, that is still better than the other weapons that sell back at a 25% loss.)  The material cost for both the Needle Mace and the War Mace is 197 gold (rounded up).<br>
<br>
Secondly, the Needle Mace is 3.4 spd and main hand only.<br>
<br>
That said, both the War Mace and the Needle Mace are very nice weapons and higher quality is always a better choice than drops (unless the drops are very high quality and have high imbue values). <p>Gwerral Darkmorn<br>
Master Crushing Mercenary<br>
Legendary Smith<br>
