While not the best quality, FL Hammers are good, quick and do reasonable damage, plus have one advantage forgotten here; they procc lke crazy at 95 dd a time.<br>
<br>
Anyone else notice that in-game weapon drop procc's seem to go off alot more than PL? My Pally has the finest PL's with DD and DOT procc's, but in dd, the drop weapons just seem to go off more often.<br>
<br>
On my second Qbar I only keep timed RA's, purge etc and accessories, prot, guard etc. and still use concussion for chases, which does slow em down, plus Flank seems very forgiving as to what it terms &quot;side of target&quot;, I've used it just about from everywhere...<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
